{"tid":190090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國發左70支導彈攻擊敘利亞","createTime":"2017-04-07T01:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T03:32:01.000Z","uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4ce1fad095d1127bfd2c621d0e1b2884f69a54","tid":190090,"uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲有多d資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇緊CNN 但英文mama<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467d77c019002e4de66b55c15f57595778a36353","tid":190090,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"美國向敘政府軍基地發射六十枚戰斧導彈<br />\n<br />\n07.04.2017 09:24<br />\n<br />\n美軍向敘利亞政府軍空軍基地，發射大約六十枚戰斧巡航導彈，以回應敘利亞北部遭受化武襲擊。華府官員說，發射導彈是要懲罰巴沙爾政權，以及破壞政府軍空軍基地。美英等國指控巴沙爾政權動用化武，導致超過八十人死亡，但敘利亞政府否認，強調他們戰機空襲反對派據點時，炸中反對派儲存化武的彈藥庫。<span style=\"color: red;\">美國總統特朗普早前指，事件令他對敘利亞的態度有非常大的改變，又說目前敘利亞目前由巴沙爾，預料敘利亞會有一些事發生。美國傳媒報道，特朗普研究對敘利亞採取軍事行動。</span>"},{"pid":"6a41bf6d3a339cff279c949bbc5e5177be12a825","tid":190090,"uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:48:16.000Z","msg":"Cnn直播：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TO85tsKemDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTO85tsKemDg&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e1287e64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TO85tsKemDg</a>"},{"pid":"af97d8e307880cafcc17ad208204ea89365c05c1","tid":190090,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"派唔派地面部隊先<br />\n<br />\nbtw習近平而家同trump開緊會,有無關係呢"},{"pid":"92053493bfd40684c6ef311e8969bda10e545b0d","tid":190090,"uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>派唔派地面部隊先<br />\n<br />\nbtw習近平而家同trump開緊會,有無關係呢</block